	(text_box "DRV8830 is limited to 1A and its output voltage maximum is its input voltage. Consider replacing with another motor driver / configurable current driver, such as the DRV8215. Note that this should be combined with a boost converter. Ideally, we need a programmable bidirectional current or voltage source that can source voltages above its input voltage if necessary."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
